				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Very glad you enjoyed it and got something from it &#8211; I was very unsure of it and had a lot of problems with it. Glad you got the courtroom vs stand-up ambiguity which was the point.</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

				<div class="reply"><a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='http://localhost:8888/microfiction.co.za/2011/02/04/comics-hearing/?replytocom=1194#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm( "div-comment-1194", "1194", "respond", "717" )' aria-label='Reply to elementalsystems'>Reply</a></div>			</article><!-- .comment-body -->
